2011-08-05T16:20:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-05/oakland-raiders-sign-ex-new-york-giants-tight-end-kevin-boss-espn-reports.html
The Oakland Raiders signed free-agent
tight end Kevin Boss to a four-year contract worth $16 million,
ESPN reported, citing an unidentified National Football League
official.  Boss, 27, caught 35 passes for 531 yards and five
touchdowns last season.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jay Beberman at 
 jbeberman@bloomberg.net  